# Abstract: 
#   this script runs a global 3DVAR multivariate analysis
#   the analysis is performed on the global HYCOM tri-polar grid
#   grid resoltuion is 8 km at the equator
#                                                                             #
# Sub-scripts called:                                                         #
#                                                                             #
